WEBVTT

00:04.193 --> 00:06.494
This is Oliver Crane
coming to you live

00:06.562 --> 00:08.696
from the Crescent City,
where, as promised,

00:08.765 --> 00:11.332
I'm meeting an anonymous source
who's gonna blow the lid off

00:11.400 --> 00:15.202
this sordid case of murder,
deception and conspiracy.

00:15.271 --> 00:17.505
Tonight I'm gonna shine a light
into the darkness.

00:17.573 --> 00:19.340
I'm going to expose
the criminals

00:19.408 --> 00:20.908
behind this
heinous killing spree,

00:20.977 --> 00:23.477
and you're gonna be there
while I do it.

00:23.546 --> 00:25.557
I'm gonna meet the one witness
who can confirm everything

00:25.581 --> 00:26.892
that local
law enforcement officials

00:26.916 --> 00:28.549
have repeatedly denied.

00:28.618 --> 00:30.985
Tonight, with her help,
everything's gonna change.

00:31.053 --> 00:32.052
Mr. Crane.

00:34.724 --> 00:36.657
Oh! Oh, my God.
Oh, my God, they shot her!

00:36.726 --> 00:38.103
They're-they're trying
to silence us.

00:38.127 --> 00:39.693
Oh, my God! If you get this...

00:39.762 --> 00:40.928
if you get this, send help!

00:40.997 --> 00:42.930
Send help right now.
No! Oh!

00:42.999 --> 00:43.133
Aah!

