01:22.138 --> 01:23.437
I like this house better, too.

01:23.506 --> 01:25.039
Mm-hmm.
It's cozy, you know?

01:25.107 --> 01:27.975
Mm-hmm.
Just needs more stuff.

01:28.044 --> 01:29.877
We can go shopping
this weekend.

01:31.314 --> 01:33.447
Okay, go brush.
