Hey.

41:24.232 --> 41:25.307
Like I said,

41:25.308 --> 41:26.507
piece of cake.

41:26.576 --> 41:29.210
Oh, my God, you got an
A-plus on your math test!

41:29.278 --> 41:31.045
Mm-hmm.

